                  </hi>. I live at 2, Hayes Buildings, Broadway, Hackney—the</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="187109180026"></xptr>
               <p>prisoner occupied my first-floor front room—there are two rooms on that floor.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined.</hi> There are four rooms and a wash-house in my house—there are no other lodgers, I and my family occupy the rest of the rooms—a woman lived with the prisoner as his wife.</p>
